  "description_snippet": "##### VULNERABILITY DETAILS\nChrome on Android translates WebGPU shaders to SPIR-V. These SPIR-V shaders are eventually passed to libGLES_mali.so for optimization and native code generation. This bug report is about a WebGPU shader that crashes org.chromium.chrome on an MTE-enable device. Chromium us"
